\id 3JN  - Dano NT [aso] -Papua New Guinea 1989 (DBL -2014) 
\h 3 ZOHANEꞌ 
\toc1 Zohaneꞌ Gizineꞌ Luhuvo Niteꞌ Naba 3 
\toc2 3 Zohaneꞌ 
\toc3 3 Zon 
\mt1 ZOHANEꞌ GIZINEꞌ LUHUVO NITEꞌ NABA 3  
\c 1  
\s1 Gaioꞌni Luhuvo Niteꞌ Gize Imineꞌ Gamazi  
\p
\v 1 Zogone lamineꞌ Gaio gaza luꞌne gimuve make, gizebo ve naza luhuvo niteꞌ nogize gimuze. Ningezo.   
\p
\v 2 Zogone, luka do lamineꞌ ogo nanivo okongasi aꞌmineꞌmine ogo ha lamineꞌ minavo minevoꞌ alevoka laminekovoꞌ o-do vo minelive lo Oꞌmosola laaꞌ nouve.  
\v 3 Leze zuho malite igi gamazi gihileꞌmi akaloꞌ vaaꞌ nane li idoꞌ gamazi gihile do giliꞌ lo minaaꞌ nane li geiꞌ monovoka li sotoꞌ igi li-nimikevo muluꞌneuꞌ lamineꞌ goloso gelo minuvoniꞌ ve.  
\v 4 Initeꞌ neꞌmine manaꞌmine initekumuꞌ muluꞌneuꞌ lamineꞌ geleloniꞌza neniꞌ izipahaꞌne zuho gamazi gihileꞌmi akaloꞌ vaaꞌ nave li likevo gelo atoꞌ nitekumuꞌ lamineꞌ gelaaꞌ nouvoniꞌ nene ivileꞌ ogo muluꞌneuꞌ lamineꞌ goloso gelaaꞌ nouve.   
\s1 Gaioꞌ Gono Lamineꞌ Davo Opoꞌni Laniꞌ Gamazi Gizineꞌ  
\p
\v 5 Zogone, Gaza leze aleve Izesuꞌ zuho ma venenga ve minanikisi lengita igaꞌ igaꞌ avo ngeleꞌmize lamineꞌ olosa gono daaꞌ naineꞌ nene monovo gihile lamineꞌ daaꞌ nane.  
\v 6 Luka ngemaningumuꞌ nene aꞌmine aleve nete Izesuꞌ evenele mulise milanguꞌ li sotoꞌ igi gopoꞌni laaꞌ nave. Idoꞌ aꞌneꞌmine aleve lengita igi nivavo ma Oꞌmosoꞌmo gelavo lisiheꞌ lamineꞌ ilidoꞌ do molo akala vilizanguꞌ initeꞌ ma viseꞌ ilizaniꞌ initeꞌ nene do sotoꞌ ogo ngemo ngeleꞌmizo vilineꞌ nene lamineꞌ oloseive.  
\v 7 Ee, Izesuꞌ guvele monelingumuꞌ gono dalone li engiꞌ misuboꞌine huli vi Izesuꞌnimuꞌ gilamavetida gono di engitatiꞌ meni disaꞌmanako hize eleꞌ o-ngedelineꞌ nene lamineꞌ o neive.  
\v 8 Nemuꞌ nene gamazi gihile di hutileꞌ ilizanguꞌ lazasi gono makatoꞌ duneꞌ gelavo mineloningumuꞌ ve lo aꞌneꞌmine ve hize eleꞌ o-ngedeloneꞌ o neive.   
\s1 Dioteleheꞌ Monovoꞌve Goloso O Vivo Demetelioꞌ Monovoꞌve Lamineꞌ Miningumuꞌ Gizineꞌ Gamazi  
\p
\v 9 Lengiꞌ muliseloꞌ luhuvo niteꞌ ma gizuvoniꞌza lengiꞌ vovotinguꞌ ve naba loloꞌ olosa amuzo molaaꞌ ive Dioteleheꞌ aza nene neniꞌ gamaziꞌne gele hulaaꞌ neive.  
\v 10 Nemuꞌ nene aza ogaꞌ ineꞌ initekumuꞌ vo lo sotoꞌ ogo eita gamazi gono dalosuve. Lelikumuꞌ gamazi goloso gehepeve lo soza gamazi lo-ledaaꞌ neive. Idoꞌ neevoꞌ nomive. Leze zuho Izesuꞌ aleve ma lengita ngimiselekunivo vi hetelikevo aza meseꞌ aseka lo-ngedesaꞌmive. Idoꞌ malite meseꞌ aseka lo-ngedelone li lilisa naavo oꞌve lo-ngedo monoꞌ muliseutiꞌ hulo heta o-ngedaaꞌ neive.   
\p
\v 11 Zogone lamine, eveneꞌ ma goloso niteꞌ di nizavo ma aꞌmidoꞌ ngeꞌmetamozo. Initeꞌ lamineꞌ di nizavo ma nelokovoꞌ ngeꞌmetezo. Ingine initeꞌ lamineꞌ di minaaꞌ nave nene Oꞌmosolatiꞌ sotoꞌ aniꞌ ve. Idoꞌ ingine goloso niteꞌ di minaaꞌ nave ingine mo Oꞌmosomuꞌ ningi gilamave.  
\v 12 Demetelioꞌnimuꞌ eveneꞌ mukiꞌ gamangi mili-daaꞌ navo gamazi gihile neꞌmosi gamangi molo-daaꞌ neive. Nazasi ezemuꞌ gamangi nomolo-duve. Idoꞌ gamazi laminekovoꞌ noluvoniꞌ nene gele nane.   
\s1 Eveneꞌ nGopoꞌni Lo-ngidineꞌ Gamazi  
\p
\v 13 Naza gamazi lo-gemeloniꞌ nene mukiꞌ ha neineꞌza gizesoꞌ gaꞌne nisamive.  
\v 14 Naza gamene haꞌna minamo geiꞌ vo ninguvo vetedunuꞌ gamazi lo voleloꞌ meloꞌ ogo minelosive losa noluve.  
\v 15 Oꞌmosoꞌmi hongu geita mineꞌmo vo minelive. Zogole zuho gopoꞌni nilave. Idoꞌ zogole zuho aꞌmida nizaniꞌ nene vo lo-ngemezo. Engiꞌ hamoꞌ hamokumuꞌ ngopoꞌni noluve. Moda ve.   